This is the markup source taken from http://qitba.qa/en/ and modified.
The initial modifications are mainly changing the asset directories and adjusting the html accordingly.

Changes
Add .html to navigation links
Changed the directory representations for assets in markup and styles
The language flip is implemented per page and will work only on server. Code written in js/functions.min.js


Deployment Notes
- Get the backup of existing source
- Make sure Arabic translation of all pages are working as expected.
- Make sure that the HTML extension is being masked


Reference
https://alexcican.com/post/how-to-remove-php-html-htm-extensions-with-htaccess/
